2010-11-29  Daniel P. Berrange  <berrange@redhat.com>

	Fix memory leaks in audit & VirtualBox code
	* src/util/virtaudit.c: Free audit string
	* src/vbox/vbox_XPCOMCGlue.c: Free library name

