2010-03-15  Sharadha Prabhakar  <sharadha.prabhakar@citrix.com>

	xenapi: Initial commit of the new driver

2010-03-13  Matthias Bolte  <matthias.bolte@googlemail.com>

	esx: Improve documentation about remote URIs

