	  qemuMonitorGetBlockStatsInfo() command
	* src/qemu/qemu_driver.c: Remove directly use of blockstats in
	  favour of calling qemuMonitorGetBlockStatsInfo()

	Add APIs for issuing 'memsave' and 'pmemsave' monitor commands
