	  qemuMonitorStopCPUs() API
	* src/qemu/qemu_driver.c: Replace direct monitor commands for 'stop'
	  with qemuMonitorStopCPUs()

	Rename qemudMonitorSendCont to qemuMonitorStartCPUs
